<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 17 Jul 2024 12:24:29 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>由于担心美国收紧对中国的销售限制，芯片股下跌</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/chip-stocks-tumble-fears-tighter-us-curbs-sales-china-2024-07-17/</link><description>周三盘前，芯片制造商股价下跌逾 4%，原因是有报道称可能对主要市场中国的先进技术供应实施更严格的限制，以及共和党总统候选人唐纳德·特朗普对台湾的评论。</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Jul 2024 12:20:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/chip-stocks-tumble-fears-tighter-us-curbs-sales-china-2024-07-17/</guid></item><item><title>活动人士呼吁英国政府阻止 Shein 在伦敦上市</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/campaigners-call-uk-government-block-sheins-london-listing-2024-07-17/</link><description>英国零售顾问兼电视名人玛丽·波塔斯(Mary Portas)支持的一项新活动发起了一份在线请愿书，呼吁新工党政府阻止快时尚零售商 Shein 在伦敦上市。</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Jul 2024 12:14:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/campaigners-call-uk-government-block-sheins-london-listing-2024-07-17/</guid></item><item><title>世贸组织称中国的产业支持计划缺乏透明度</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-industrial-support-programmes-lack-transparency-wto-says-2024-07-17/</link><description>世界贸易组织周三表示，由于“总体缺乏透明度”，它无法清楚了解中国对电动汽车或铝和钢铁生产等关键工业部门的财政支持。</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Jul 2024 12:06:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-industrial-support-programmes-lack-transparency-wto-says-2024-07-17/</guid></item><item><title>共和党资深议员要求拜登提供在北京僵局中支持菲律宾的选择</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/senior-republican-lawmakers-ask-biden-options-support-philippines-beijing-2024-07-17/</link><description>美国两名高级共和党参议员要求乔·拜登总统提供五角大楼和国务院制定的完整选项清单，以帮助支持菲律宾最近与北京因南海争议浅滩发生的对峙。</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Jul 2024 12:04:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us/senior-republican-lawmakers-ask-biden-options-support-philippines-beijing-2024-07-17/</guid></item><item><title>戴姆勒卡车股价在指导警告后下跌</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/daimler-truck-shares-fall-after-guidance-warning-2024-07-17/</link><description>德国戴姆勒卡车公司公布其在欧洲销售的卡车的利润率低于预期，并表示其今年的指引目前正在“审查中”，该公司股价周三下跌 4.2%。</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Jul 2024 12:01:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/daimler-truck-shares-fall-after-guidance-warning-2024-07-17/</guid></item><item><title>许多美国太阳能工厂都处于落后状态。除了中国拥有的</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/many-us-solar-factories-are-lagging-except-those-china-owns-2024-07-17/</link><description>中国公司在美国兴建的太阳能制造厂数量激增，使中国在这一新兴行业占据主导地位，而其他美国工厂尽管有联邦补贴，仍难以参与竞争。</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Jul 2024 10:11:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/many-us-solar-factories-are-lagging-except-those-china-owns-2024-07-17/</guid></item><item><title>中国在美国拥有的太阳能工厂</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/chinese-owned-solar-factories-united-states-2024-07-17/</link><description>得益于乔·拜登总统的 2022 年通胀削减法案中包含的新的清洁能源制造补贴，一些最大的中国太阳能电池板制造商正在美国开设工厂。</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Jul 2024 10:09:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/chinese-owned-solar-factories-united-states-2024-07-17/</guid></item><item><title>美国太阳能电池板制造商寻求更严格的“美国制造”规则</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sustainability/climate-energy/us-solar-panel-makers-seek-tougher-made-usa-rules-2024-07-17/</link><description>一群美国太阳能制造商呼吁拜登政府加强对使用国产组件的太阳能项目开发商的税收抵免规定，称他们无需使用美国太阳能电池板即可获得税收抵免。</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Jul 2024 10:07:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sustainability/climate-energy/us-solar-panel-makers-seek-tougher-made-usa-rules-2024-07-17/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：小盘股追赶轮换飙升，特朗普震慑台湾</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-07-17/</link><description>迈克·多兰 (Mike Dolan) 对美国和全球市场未来一天的展望</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Jul 2024 10:05:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-07-17/</guid></item><item><title>美俄新一轮导弹竞赛有多危险？</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/arms-race-gathers-pace-russia-us-plan-redeploy-once-banned-weapons-2024-07-17/</link><description>四十年前，美国在欧洲部署了巡航导弹和潘兴 II 核导弹，以对抗苏联的 SS-20 导弹——这一举动加剧了冷战紧张局势，但在几年内就达成了一项历史性的裁军协议。</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Jul 2024 09:27:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/arms-race-gathers-pace-russia-us-plan-redeploy-once-banned-weapons-2024-07-17/</guid></item><item><title>消息人士称，印度希望为中国技术人员免签</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/india/india-looks-free-up-visas-chinese-technicians-sources-say-2024-07-17/</link><description>三名政府官员表示，印度预计将加快向中国技术人员发放签证的进程，因为印度希望克服制造部门的延误，这些延误阻碍了数十亿美元的投资。</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Jul 2024 08:32:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/india/india-looks-free-up-visas-chinese-technicians-sources-say-2024-07-17/</guid></item><item><title>欧盟法院称字节跳动必须保留看门人标签以提振监管机构</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/eu-court-rejects-bytedances-challenge-against-eu-gatekeeper-label-2024-07-17/</link><description>周三，TikTok 母公司字节跳动在针对其根据具有里程碑意义的欧盟规则被指定为看门人的法庭诉讼中败诉，这为反垄断监管机构寻求遏制大型科技公司的权力提供了动力。</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Jul 2024 08:07:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/eu-court-rejects-bytedances-challenge-against-eu-gatekeeper-label-2024-07-17/</guid></item><item><title>“垃圾时间”：中国经济衰退催生经济绝望的新模因</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/garbage-time-chinas-slump-spins-out-new-meme-economic-despair-2024-07-17/</link><description>中国经济萎靡不振，在网上引发了一种可怕的新说法，用来形容对就业、收入和机会好转前景的悲观情绪：“历史的垃圾时期”。</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Jul 2024 08:05:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/garbage-time-chinas-slump-spins-out-new-meme-economic-despair-2024-07-17/</guid></item><item><title>独家：菲律宾和中国将建立新渠道处理南海争端</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-china-set-up-new-channels-handle-south-china-sea-rows-source-2024-07-17/</link><description>据一份文件和菲律宾外交消息人士称，随着中菲关系因南海领土冲突而恶化，菲律宾和中国已同意建立新的沟通渠道，以改善两国对海上争端的处理。</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Jul 2024 07:27:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-china-set-up-new-channels-handle-south-china-sea-rows-source-2024-07-17/</guid></item><item><title>由于美联储降息的希望，亚洲债券连续第二个月出现外资流入</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/rates-bonds/asian-bonds-see-foreign-inflows-second-month-hopes-fed-rate-cut-2024-07-17/</link><description>受通胀水平缓和和劳动力市场状况降温的美联储降息预期的提振，外国人在 6 月份连续第二个月成为亚洲债券的净投资者。</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Jul 2024 06:35:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/rates-bonds/asian-bonds-see-foreign-inflows-second-month-hopes-fed-rate-cut-2024-07-17/</guid></item></channel></rss>